            <xsd:annotation>
               <xsd:documentation>
				NPE is capable of processing  REL to USA, ACGU correctly. 
				NPE users consists of persons who have one of AUS, CAN, GBR, USA countryOfAffiliation and appropriate adminOrganization.
				NPE is NOT capable of distinguishing between it's users based on countryOfAffiliation so the minimum REL must be ACGU.
			</xsd:documentation>
            </xsd:annotation>
         </xsd:enumeration>
