			</xsd:documentation>
            </xsd:annotation>
         </xsd:enumeration>
         <xsd:enumeration value="REL_FVEY">
            <xsd:annotation>
               <xsd:documentation>
				NPE is capable of processing REL to USA, FVEY correctly. 
				NPE users consists of persons who have one of AUS, CAN, GBR, NZL, USA countryOfAffiliation and appropriate adminOrganization.
